snippet.title: Easy Peanut Butter Ice Cream
snippet.description: Your kids will treasure every bite of this delicious peanut butter ice cream.

snippet.title: Fettuccine with Creamy Tomato Vodka Sauce
snippet.description: The subtle blending of tomatoes, cream and vodka make this indulgent fettuccine dish sophisticated enough for unexpected company yet quick and comforting for everyday fare.

snippet.title: Pick-Me-Up Pumpkin Latte
snippet.description: Enjoy this coffeehouse-style Pick-Me-Up Pumpkin Latte drink anytime. Pumpkin melts right into the coffee and adds body and natural flavor. Creamy fat free evaporated milk adds richness and calcium, without adding extra fat. This is a great satisfying specialty beverage for all year round.

snippet.title: Macadamia Nut White Chip Pumpkin Cookies
snippet.description: Macadamia Nut White Chip Pumpkin Cookies are a crunchy, rich and wonderful cookie. Pumpkin adds a luscious moistness to these year-round favorites.

snippet.title: Pumpkin Dutch Apple Pie
snippet.description: This Pumpkin Dutch Apple Pie recipe features a layer of crisp, crunchy apples topped with creamy pumpkin sprinkled with a crumble topping. It is just what the doctor ordered for those suffering from pumpkin-apple deficiency. Serve with a generous smile and slices of sharp cheddar cheese.

snippet.title: Easy Toffee Candy
snippet.description: Easy and delicious candy to make that all in the family will enjoy!

snippet.title: Pumpkin Apple Bread
snippet.description: This moist, flavorful and nutritious Pumpkin Apple Bread is a perfect pack-along for school lunches, picnics and tailgating festivities. Grated orange peel and ground cinnamon add a wonderful flavor dimension to this easy-to-make and versatile bread.

snippet.title: Fruity Yogurt Pops
snippet.description: These Fruity Yogurt Pops make a refreshing summertime treat! Yogurt is a great alternative, and these pops can be enjoyed any time of year.

snippet.title: Sour Milk Made with Carnation Evaporated Milk
snippet.description: Sour Milk Made with Carnation Evaporated Milk is a great alternative to buttermilk to give your recipes that tang!

snippet.title: Cream of Broccoli Soup
snippet.description: The homemade goodness of this Cream of Broccoli Soup will satisfy any appetite.
